{{#section "subject"}}
Your Iris Account Was Logged Into From A New Device
{{/section}}

{{#section "plaintext-body"}}
Hi {{{_person.firstName}}},

A new mobile device was used to sign into your Iris account. If you 
are aware of this change, please disregard this email.

By default, this device will now receive your push notifications. 
Edit these settings by going to Settings > Profile > Push Notifications.

If you did not recently sign into your Iris account from a new mobile 
device, your account may have been compromised.
{{/section}}

